      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育LMS门户设计一个完整的Token生命周期状态图。核心场景是：学生登录后系统生成双Token——AccessToken无状态、RefreshToken有状态，后者需要入库管理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Login",
        "TokensGenerated",
        "AccessToken_Stateless",
        "RefreshToken_Stateful"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我注意到TokensGenerated是一个复合状态，里面包含两个并行子状态：GradeSync对接AccessToken、ContentCDN对接RefreshToken。这样画对吗？另外AccessToken有效期15分钟这个细节要体现吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TokensGenerated",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "AccessToken_Stateless",
        "RefreshToken_Stateful",
        "Active",
        "Expired"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，15分钟有效期必须标出来，这是安全关键。AccessToken走Active→Expired的流转，Expired之后必须能用RefreshToken续期，不能让学生重新登录。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AccessToken_Stateless",
        "Active",
        "Expired",
        "Refresh",
        "RefreshToken_Stateful"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "RefreshToken这边我设计了四层状态：入库后7天有效，触发Refresh RPC时进入Rotated，此时旧Token要标记删除、同时签发新Token对重新入库。另外管理员调用DeleteUser时要能强制Revoked。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RefreshToken_Stateful",
