      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "Rotated到StoredInDB的箭头描述需要调整——不是\"New Token Pair Issued\"，应该是\"New Token Pair Issued\"作为动作标签，但目标状态还是StoredInDB。另外Revoked之后要回到ContentCDN表示清理完成，这个终点关系别漏了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rotated",
        "StoredInDB",
        "New Token Pair Issued",
