      "utterance": "收到，已修正Rotated→StoredInDB的标注为\"New Token Pair Issued\"，并补全Revoked到ContentCDN的终止连线。还有Expired到StudentDB的关联需要保留吗？看起来像是数据归档路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rotated",
        "StoredInDB",
